author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-RaySearch says wins orders worth $6.4 mln in North America​
text:
March 31 (Reuters) - RaySearch Laboratories Ab (Publ) :
* SAYS ‍TWO MAJOR ORDERS FOR RAYSTATION FROM NORTH AMERICA​
* SAYS ‍COMBINED ORDER VALUE OF 6.4 MUSD (EXCLUDING SERVICE AGREEMENTS), CORRESPONDING TO APPROXIMATELY 53 MSEK, HAS TO A LARGE EXTENT BEEN DELIVERED AND IS EXPECTED TO GENERATE REVENUE OF APPROXIMATELY 38 MSEK IN Q1 OF 2018
* SAYS THE REMAINING ORDER VALUE WILL GENERATE REVENUE DURING THE COMING 15 MONTHS.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reporting By Stockholm newsroom)
